description: Below are the rest of the pig dongers that didn’t fit in the other few categories. There are just so many pig emoticons and I couldn’t stand the thought of leaving any of them out! These pig snouts are triangles or other complex characters that do not show up in every browser. If you are having problems seeing these miscellaneous pig emoticons, try switching over to Safari.
